{"tid":1173124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港仔的士掃欄撞斷紅綠燈　多人倒地重傷","createTime":"2019-05-27T01:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T03:31:31.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"232313834ccb87523ef27c0d311c520894536b8b","tid":1173124,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"【09:35】運輸署宣布，受意外影響，香港仔大道往黃竹坑方向近香港仔水塘道的全線現已封閉，上址交通繁忙。<br />\n<br />\n香港仔大道近洛陽街發生交通意外，今早(27日)9時許，一輛的士往香港仔隧道方向行駛，期間失控掃毀鐵欄剷上行人路，撞斷紅綠燈，以致至少6人受傷，其中一人大量流血，陷入昏迷，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20190527/photo/bkn-20190527091929234-0527_00942_001_02b.jpg?20190527094904\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20190527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190527091929234-0527_00942_001_02b.jpg%3F20190527094904&h=67663038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20190527/photo/bkn-20190527091929234-0527_00942_001_03b.jpg?20190527094904\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20190527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190527091929234-0527_00942_001_03b.jpg%3F20190527094904&h=e643551f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b095b19ea431bfe546cf596662df95849fbccfb","tid":1173124,"uid":4826,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"又係DC狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次又嫌人$24?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c425d45d4e3645651585f4b8a460d92d3e903f","tid":1173124,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84616a8432e40a63ee9d4fa8b07a42e008a86dca","tid":1173124,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"DC9真係馬路炸彈"},{"pid":"3b82b998b54bb4e43c3f78e4e0afd6d5da3049a6","tid":1173124,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1